* Martin D W Jones, &#x27;The War of Lost Footsteps. A Re-assessment of the Third Burmese War 1885–1896.&#x27;, The Bulletin of the Military Historical Society, xxxx no. 157 (August 1989), pp. 36–40
*The Register of the Victoria Cross (This England, 1997)
*The Sapper VCs (Gerald Napier, 1998)
*Monuments to Courage (David Harvey, 1999)

